cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with generating images from text captions. It also involves attention mechanisms, which are commonly used in computer vision tasks. It could also belong to the natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-category as it involves generating visual-semantic sentence embeddings based on self-attention over text. The paper also introduces a new method for generating these embeddings, which could fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, since the paper deals with generating images, it could also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
